         <abstract>
            <p>We give a piecewise cubic curve fitting algorithm which preserves monotonicity of the data. The algorithm has a higher order of convergence than the Fritsch-Carlson algorithm and is simpler than the Eisenstat-Jackson-Lewis algorithm.</p>
          </abstract>
